      <title>银行破坏了私人信贷创纪录的阿多纳交易 20 亿美元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/banks-spoil-private-credit-s-record-ardonagh-deal-with-2-billion-bond</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Ardonagh Group Ltd. 计划最早于周一发行 20 亿美元的债券，这是银行战胜私人信贷公司的一次关键胜利，后者曾向这家英国保险公司提供了创纪录的 50 亿美元贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/banks-spoil-private-credit-s-record-ardonagh-deal-with-2-billion-bond</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 02:28:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管北京承诺保持稳定，中国股市仍大幅波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/china-stocks-languish-despite-renewed-vow-to-stabilize-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[继上周暴跌后，中国股市周一再次陷入波动，投资者评估了政策制定者稳定暴跌股市的最新承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/china-stocks-languish-despite-renewed-vow-to-stabilize-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 01:50:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
