      <title>美国对胡塞武装的袭击加剧紧张局势，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国誓言对伊朗军队和代理人进行更多打击，而胡塞武装承诺对周末的轰炸进行报复，油价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 23:26:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔和中国小型股下滑导致美国国债下跌：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/treasury-selloff-hits-asia-on-pared-rate-cut-bets-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，政策制定者可能会等到三月之后再降息，随后美国国债延续了周五的抛售。尽管有官方支持的迹象，但市场不安情绪持续存在，中国小盘股下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/treasury-selloff-hits-asia-on-pared-rate-cut-bets-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 22:33:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>飓风和大雨袭击加州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/california-storm-coast-to-be-battered-by-high-winds-heavy-rain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[飓风强度的大风席卷了加利福尼亚州的海域，而另一场强大的太平洋风暴袭击了该州，暴雨增加了从旧金山到圣地亚哥的洪水风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/california-storm-coast-to-be-battered-by-high-winds-heavy-rain</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 13:49:47 GMT</pubDate>
